Come on. Quick. quick. quick.

1282
01:33:08.398 --> 01:33:09.733
All right? Let's go.

1283
01:33:09.816 --> 01:33:11.735
Quick. quick. quick!
Come on!

1284
01:33:18.033 --> 01:33:20.744
All right. Come on.
