1434
01:46:19.605 --> 01:46:22.233
We gotta go.
Come on. Let's go.

1435
01:46:38.040 --> 01:46:39.542
There! There they are!

1436
01:46:39.625 --> 01:46:42.420
- Help us!
- Hey! Hey!

1437
01:46:44.255 --> 01:46:46.090
- Look. look! They see us!
- Come on.

1438
01:46:55.433 --> 01:46:57.435
Let's go!

1439
