Blast doors closing.

1450
01:48:07.463 --> 01:48:09.131
Let's go. let's go!

1451
01:48:09.215 --> 01:48:11.467
- Go. go. go!
- Blast doors closing.

1452
01:48:13.636 --> 01:48:15.763
